room_title: Escape room "Escape from Wonderland" by Escape Room Adventures WNY in Buffalo
room_description: You and your group of wanderers have stumbled into Wonderland. Alice and the other inhabitants are nowhere to be found, but they left clues for you to follow. With the Queen of Hearts breathing murderous threats down your neck, make your way through this whimsical room full of riddles, tea, puzzles, games, and a bit of danger.
